<div class="container py-5">
    <div class="text-center">
        <h1 class="display-4 fw-bold" style="color:limegreen">About Us</h1>
        <p class="text-muted">Get to know more about FarmSquare and our team</p>
        <hr class="my-4 w-50 mx-auto">
    </div>

    <div class="my-5">
        <h2 class="fw-bold" style="color:limegreen">FarmSquare - Your Trusted Farm Products Marketplace</h2>
        <p class="lead">
            At <strong>FarmSquare</strong>, we are committed to bridging the gap between local farmers and customers who seek fresh, high-quality farm products. 
            Our platform empowers small and medium-scale farmers to reach a broader audience, ensuring sustainable growth and fair pricing.
        </p>
        <p>
            We believe in supporting local communities, promoting sustainable farming practices, and delivering the freshest produce right to your doorstep. 
            FarmSquare is not just an app—it's a movement towards a healthier, greener, and more connected future.
        </p>
    </div>

    <div class="my-5">
