        <div class="row g-4">
            <div class="col-lg-4 text-center">
                <div class="p-4 shadow-sm border rounded">
                    <h5 class="fw-bold mb-3">Sooraj Chowki</h5>
                    <p>Lead Developer</p>
                    <p class="text-muted">Passionate about creating seamless digital experiences, Sooraj leads the technical development of FarmSquare.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-4 text-center">
                <div class="p-4 shadow-sm border rounded">
                    <h5 class="fw-bold mb-3">Swarup Shetty</h5>
                    <p>Full-Stack Developer</p>
                    <p class="text-muted">Swarup focuses on building the robust back-end systems and user-friendly interfaces that make FarmSquare so efficient.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-4 text-center">
                <div class="p-4 shadow-sm border rounded">
                    <h5 class="fw-bold mb-3">Lakshmiprasad</h5>
                    <p>Full-Stack and UI/UX Designer</p>
                    <p class="text-muted">Lakshmiprasad ensures that FarmSquare is not only functional but also visually appealing and easy to navigate.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="my-5">
        <h2 class="fw-bold" style="color:limegreen">Our Vision</h2>
        <p class="lead">
            To create a platform that supports local farmers, encourages sustainable practices, and ensures customers have access to fresh, high-quality farm products.
        </p>
        <p>
            At FarmSquare, we envision a world where technology enhances agriculture, making it more sustainable and equitable for everyone involved.
        </p>
    </div>

    <div class="text-center my-5">
